    "2a) used CNNs to process matched tumor and normal reads to catalog somatic mutations.",
    "A similar approach was used by Krishnamachari et al. [84] (Fig.",
    "2a) three years later.",
    "Both methods displayed superior accuracy compared to conventional bioinformatic tools.",
    "Nevertheless, the large amount of training data and high computing power needed for DL could hinder its broad adoption."
